This is the repository showing us in setting up the GitHub Actions workflow.

###########################
# github-actions-terraform
###########################

github-actions-terraform with tools that are used:
==================================================
This is the project structure of the demo.In this project we are using tfsec and tflint for terraform.

* TFLint -finding potential errors and violations of best practices in your Terraform configurations before you apply them.
* Tfsec  -This tool uses static analysis of your terraform code to spot potential security issues.

How to install tfsec and tflint is below. Refer to the open source git repo,

https://github.com/terraform-linters/tflint
https://github.com/aquasecurity/tfsec

